text:
(1) Highbridge Park: The tower and reservoir as viewed eastward from Amsterdam Ave., at the foot of West 173rd Street. This view shows the reservoir under demolition. October 30, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same as No. 1. November 5, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) A view of same in a westward direction as seen from the bridge that carries the water tubes across the Harlem River. April 8, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
